<sect1 id="dir_c44faea763af7288aeca8677f94fea29_1autotoc_md699">
<title>Flush Routing</title><para>During <computeroutput>TypedCommandBuffer::flush()</computeroutput>, each command type is processed in template parameter order:</para>
<para>1. <bold>Handler route:</bold> If a handler for <computeroutput>Cmd</computeroutput> is registered in the <computeroutput>CommandHandlerRegistry</computeroutput>, all queued commands are submitted to the handler via the stored function pointer. 2. <bold>Direct execution:</bold> Otherwise, if the command satisfies <computeroutput>ExecutableCommand</computeroutput>, it executes itself 3. <bold>Assertion:</bold> If neither applies, an assertion fires (misconfiguration)</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_c44faea763af7288aeca8677f94fea29_1autotoc_md700">
<title>Usage</title><para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Spawn<sp/>command<sp/>with<sp/>context</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">SpawnContext<sp/>ctx;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ctx.emitterContext<sp/>=<sp/>EmitterContext{position,<sp/>velocity};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">commandBuffer.add&lt;SpawnCommand&gt;(bulletProfileId,<sp/>ctx,<sp/>1);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Despawn<sp/>command</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">commandBuffer.add&lt;DespawnCommand&gt;(entityGuid,<sp/>profileId);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Scheduled<sp/>spawn<sp/>plan<sp/>command<sp/>(from<sp/>SpawnScheduler)</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">commandBuffer.add&lt;ScheduledSpawnPlanCommand&gt;(std::move(scheduledPlan));</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
